Introduction

Eunjung, also known as Elsie, is a South Korean singer and actress currently under Mask Studio and Likey Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group T-ARA and its sub-unit T-ARA N4. On May 2015, she made her solo debut as Elsie with mini album "I'm Good".

Her contract with MBK Entertainment ended in December 2017 and fellow member Hyo Min announced on her Instagram account that Qri, Ji Yeon and herself would leave the company. She is now focused on her Career as an Actress.

On September 27, 2021, Eunjung signed an exclusive contract with Management Koo.
